E-06 INPUT DOCK
E-07 INPUT USER PARTS NO.
E-08 INPUT PICK-UP DATE
E-09 PICK-UP DATE (YYMMDD) IS NOT RIGHT
E-10 INPUT PICK-UP TIME
E-11 PICK-UP TIME (HHSS) IS NOT RIGHT
E-12 ADD WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F EXIST
E-13 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F DON'T EXIST
E-14 CHANGE WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-15 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F DON'T EXIST
E-16 CANCEL WAS APPOINTED BUT M/F IS CANCELLED ALREADY
